AEC / Students

American Education Center has over 17 years of experience in providing unparalleled educational services to enthusiastic and motivated learners. The solutions listed below aim to eliminate education barriers for pursuing higher education in the U.S. and China:


Transfer international students to study in the US

Provide internship opportunities
Provide a setting for entrepreneurship











